name: Salma Hayek
description:
Salma Hayek Pinault (September 2, 1966) is a Mexican and American actress and film producer. She soon established herself in Hollywood with appearances in films such as Desperado (1995), From Dusk till Dawn (1996), Wild Wild West (1999), and Dogma (1999)... and a lot more.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hey everyone! Today I present you a textual inversion of Salma Hayek. I wanted to experiment with a specific time window: 7900 steps and 90 public images, but only in the 2010-2019 years. Suggestion: do not use the face restore.

To use it:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add salhayek66 to your prompt;

  • Keep the Samples around 25, CFG between 5 and 7 seems to work good. As usual, feel free to experiment;
